{"tid":1471361,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.","createTime":"2019-08-14T09:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T01:04:41.000Z","uid":228955,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"724e851dc170f6133b2424a1c0061a0a871f4b75","tid":1471361,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"British National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=fb51eb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"b91fec48f46bcd2ece31815e1325d4649cc894d7","tid":1471361,"uid":226569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:01:33.000Z","msg":"British National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=fb51eb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\nhelp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9063859c5cc35ad676c5a58f93f6019b98ca4ace","tid":1471361,"uid":226569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:03:18.000Z","msg":"【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=fb51eb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ1 : 簽咗咁多聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> / 英國佬唔會幫我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> /英國佬都唔想收咁多新移民喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/ 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Q2: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 （ ff住先）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ4: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=fb51eb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"d99f2e816b416b14eaf786c487b0661d21b51d61","tid":1471361,"uid":265772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T20:01:31.000Z","msg":"推！咁都唔夠數，搞乜！！！"},{"pid":"1fc8853beaa7fd05580827bcac4bfb8f5113a324","tid":1471361,"uid":172287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:51:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W3UBOE8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW3UBOE8.gif&h=43790ab3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"123d48391ec877478492f78fc19fba6b3747350f","tid":1471361,"uid":295889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:24:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正經post冇人推！？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Set deadline再升級係大多手足嘅共識 大家一齊去公投啦 要過5,000正評 </span></span><br />\n冇網絡大軍要靠大家！！<br />\n<br />\n【公投】民間記者會設限825通牒林奠答應訴求（係答應唔係回應！！！）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEHHFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dEHHFS</a>"},{"pid":"f36b5a857c30031f6a4473c0b0b288d4aea9ac6c","tid":1471361,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"Help"},{"pid":"194c8132334b41dfb29bd08bd5c1bac1ae5bb1c7","tid":1471361,"uid":268930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:24:26.000Z","msg":"1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overs