ttps://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=fb51eb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:14:15.000Z","msg":"// 1.成功爭取父母啲BNO變BC後, 因關係可以用家庭團聚形式入籍 //<br />\n<br />\n不過留意返，要睇父母變BC後係<strong><ins>當</ins></strong>邊一款：(1) by descent; (2) otherwise than by descent。<br />\n<br />\n如果係前者，咁根據而家既法律，父母同仔女需要過去住3年，仔女先可以攞埋BC。"},{"pid":"abbc12f50306973d42caa8959d4ac433dc20bbe5","tid":1471361,"uid":65701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"今曰慢咗咁多既？<br />\n推"},{"pid":"2fa936d44d947aa796616737f2f933ec164ef861","tid":1471361,"uid":217441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:22:38.000Z","msg":"push ar<br />\n<br />\nhelp sign it"},{"pid":"14a6acd28881881ad23e1a475734831034b33166","tid":1471361,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"57000"},{"pid":"cd960853028d61895f8ab072165a73d519c7396e","tid":1471361,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"就黎60000了<br />\n快簽<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=fb51eb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n推上國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28057a83bedf3eb93d3b193eea022f566a43e8eb","tid":1471361,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:26:04.000Z","msg":"60000"},{"pid":"50b50dec9ccafef80a66a0803d2d04c0dcc84cf6","